# pgRDF.SOURCE

The pgRDF extension this Console targets is the repository this `web/` folder
lives in (../  — styk-tv/pgRDF). Build it from the repo root; do NOT vendor a
copy here. Reunited 2026-06-25 from the sibling project-azure-pgRDF (sku/pgrdf/v0.1,
2026-05-27 — the pgRDF Console: SPARQL editor -> translated-SQL view -> graph
browser/canvas/sidebar, FastAPI + React).
